  <work>
    <work-title>While O'er Our Guilty Land, O Lord</work-title>
  </work>
  <identification>
    <creator type="composer">Words: verses 1-3, Samuel Davies, 1769. alt. verses 4-6, Brian J. Dumont, 15 Nov 2010.
Music: 'Federal Street' Henry K. Oliver, 1832.
Setting: "The Evangelical Lutheran Hymnal" (Ohio Synod), 1908.
copyright: public domain.  This score is a part of the Open Hymnal Project, 2010 Revision.</creator>
