    <source>Music source: 'The Evangelical Lutheran Hymnal' (Ohio Synod), 1908.</source>
    <miscellaneous>
      <miscellaneous-field name="lyrics">6.We are your children after all,
Redeemed by Christ after the fall.
Marked with Your Name in Baptism,
Our home remains in Your Kingdom.</miscellaneous-field>
    </miscellaneous>
  </identification>
